Note on the underlying glyph design:

This font is a Ukrainian-alphabet adaptation derived from the FIGlet font
"ANSI Shadow", which is distributed as part of the pyfiglet font collection.
The original `.flf` lists `Font Author: ?` and points to the TheDraw / RoySAC
community archive, indicating that the original author is undocumented and
the glyph design has long been treated as a community asset. The Ukrainian
glyphs added in this work are original to Pan Vena.

Pyfiglet itself (used to render the font) is MIT-licensed:
  Copyright (c) 2007-2018 Christopher Jones, Stefano Rivera, Peter Waller,
  and various contributors. https://github.com/pwaller/pyfiglet
